// Content 
.container-fluid
	+b('section').content
		+e('h1').heading.text-center Get Involved
		+b().entry
			h2 Gala Luncheon
			p The WAMS Gala Luncheon is an annual fundraising event that raises essential funds for MS research. Each year, the sold out event honours a woman who has made a difference in her community.
			p Purchase your ticket today.

			h2 WAMS Monthly Giving
			p Monthly giving allows organizations like the MS Society to create and properly plan sustainable research programs that will lead to a breakthrough or cure for multiple sclerosis.
			p We encourage you to visit <a href="#">mssociety.ca/wamsmonthly</a> to join the WAMS month giving program. Your contribution could be the one that ends MS.

			h2 Join WAMS Today
			form.contact-form(action='#', method='POST', role='form')
				.form-group
					input.form-control.input-lg(type='text', placeholder='First Name:', required)
				.form-group
					input.form-control.input-lg(type='text', placeholder='Last Name:', required)
				.form-group
					input.form-control.input-lg(type='email', placeholder='Email address:', required)
				.form-group.form-group--last
					input.form-control.input-lg(type='tel', placeholder='Phone number:', required)
				button.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block(type='submit') Submit
// Content End 

